reviews.name: Jetts Garage
reviews.text: Honestly, I left a good review because I trusted this company to make right on their word. After several months of nothing but excuse and excuses, I'm forced to change my review. I DO NOT RECOMMEND THIS COMPANY!!! Horrible Horrible Horrible. I was quoted a price of $725 for installation of 10x10 roll up door with chain hoist. After paying over half up front for the door, the guy showed up alone.....  He didn't have help to install the door, so being a nice guy I helped him. He didn't have all the tools he needed, so I loaned him mine. Even my ladder. I didn't mind this at all. I helped him lift the door up because it's too heavy for one person. The guy informed my that my chain hoist was left out of the box and he would pick it up the following week. No problem right????  I'm easy to work with. After almost a week went by, not hearing from them, I text him. He informed me the price went up an additional $200. If I wanted my chain hoist, that I already paid for, I was going to have to pay an additional $200. I WAS FURIOUS! I ended up getting them to agree to meet me in the middle at $100 from them, and $100 from me. After several months of excuses, I still have yet to get my chain hoist! The door isn't installed correctly either. I have to stick a board under it to keep it open. It won't stay open at all. The door tension was never set correctly. Please do yourself a favor, go with any other company!!!
reviews.responseFromOwnerText: Thank you
